<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You look like a zombie.
-It's just the lighting.</font>

13
00:01:08,105 --> 00:01:10,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I bet you're just eating junk, aren't you?</font>

14
00:01:10,305 --> 00:01:12,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's way better than your cooking.</font>

15
00:01:13,105 --> 00:01:14,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, I'm still sick!</font>

16
00:01:14,405 --> 00:01:16,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which is why
I'm telling you to come back home.</font>

17
00:01:19,505 --> 00:01:22,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll have a proper talk together
about your future and--</font>

18
00:01:22,905 --> 00:01:23,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No way.</font>

19
00:01:24,305 --> 00:01:25,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

20
00:01:25,405 --> 00:01:28,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, I don't think
you even have the right to talk like that.</font>

21
00:01:30,505 --> 00:01:32,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whose fault do you think it was
that I left?</font>

22
00:01:33,972 --> 00:01:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hmm? Let me think.</font>

23
00:01:36,205 --> 00:01:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hey!
-I'm just kidding.</font>

24
00:01:38,305 --> 00:01:42,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In any case,
if you're going to wreck your health</font>

25
00:01:42,405 --> 00:01:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because you're living alone,
then I'm dragging you back home.</font>

26
00:01:45,305 --> 00:01:47,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't even know where I live.</font>

27
00:01:48,305 --> 00:01:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The doctor told me.</font>

28
00:01:53,505 --> 00:01:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't help it. They asked me.</font>

29
00:01:55,505 --> 00:01:56,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You blabber.</font>

30
00:01:57,705 --> 00:02:00,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How dare you scold
the person you owe your life to?</font>

31
00:02:00,205 --> 00:02:02,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Would you cut it out with the hitting?</font>

32
00:02:02,105 --> 00:02:03,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You ungrateful smart-ass!</font>

33
00:02:03,705 --> 00:02:05,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I am <i>not ungrateful.</i></font>

34
00:02:05,072 --> 00:02:06,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then at least try to act it.</font>

35
00:02:07,039 --> 00:02:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why you!</font>

36
00:02:08,205 --> 00:02:10,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'll be going now.</font>

37
00:02:11,105 --> 00:02:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

38
00:02:14,572 --> 00:02:17,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, at least thank her.</font>

39
00:02:20,305 --> 00:02:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks... for all your help.</font>

40
00:02:25,405 --> 00:02:27,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK. Take care of yourself.</font>

41
00:02:28,705 --> 00:02:29,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

42
00:02:36,839 --> 00:02:39,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Wait a second. Let's go together.</font>

43
00:02:41,105 --> 00:02:43,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to ask you about Hisashi.</font>

44
00:02:52,105 --> 00:02:54,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to go to tell the doctor thanks.</font>

45
00:02:54,839 --> 00:02:56,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait for me in the lobby, OK?</font>

46
00:02:56,972 --> 00:02:58,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

47
00:03:01,839 --> 00:03:04,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was a wedding ring, right?</font>

48
00:03:05,605 --> 00:03:07,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! That means...</font>

49
00:03:08,405 --> 00:03:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">they're having an affair?</font>

50
00:03:34,005 --> 00:03:35,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">An affair...</font>

51
00:03:37,772 --> 00:03:41,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara and that pretty woman...</font>

52
00:03:49,939 --> 00:03:53,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We can't. I have a husband--</font>

53
00:03:55,405 --> 00:03:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri. I want you to be mine.</font>

54
00:04:01,205 --> 00:04:02,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisashi.</font>

55
00:04:07,105 --> 00:04:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, no, no!</font>

56
00:04:10,005 --> 00:04:15,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That... that's for grownups! For adults!</font>

57
00:04:15,939 --> 00:04:21,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...
Uehara seemed so right in that scene.</font>

58
00:04:25,505 --> 00:04:28,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong? Are you feeling sick?</font>

59
00:04:28,705 --> 00:04:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... no. I'm fine.</font>

60
00:04:33,205 --> 00:04:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Uehara Yuri.</font>

61
00:04:36,305 --> 00:04:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here's my card. My number's on it.</font>

62
00:04:41,505 --> 00:04:43,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

63
00:04:45,305 --> 00:04:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara</font>

64
00:04:47,072 --> 00:04:51,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I'm Hisashi's sister-in-law.</font>

65
00:04:51,672 --> 00:04:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">His older brother is Takuya.
He's my husband.</font>

66
00:04:55,972 --> 00:04:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now I see.</font>

67
00:04:58,105 --> 00:04:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

68
00:04:59,072 --> 00:05:01,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara and his sister-in-law are having
an aff...</font>

69
00:05:01,905 --> 00:05:02,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

70
00:05:05,672 --> 00:05:08,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Yoshikawa Nao.</font>

71
00:05:09,005 --> 00:05:11,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. That's a pretty name.</font>

72
00:05:13,572 --> 00:05:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for taking care of Hisashi.</font>

73
00:05:16,505 --> 00:05:17,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

74
00:05:17,472 --> 00:05:18,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're his girlfriend, right?</font>

75
00:05:18,972 --> 00:05:21,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Whose girlfriend?</font>

76
00:05:21,105 --> 00:05:22,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisashi's. You're Hisashi's girlfriend.</font>

77
00:05:23,605 --> 00:05:27,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, no! Not at all. We're just classmates.</font>

78
00:05:27,505 --> 00:05:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Really?</font>

79
00:05:30,039 --> 00:05:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's unusual.</font>

80
00:05:31,305 --> 00:05:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's not many people
he's that relaxed with</font>

81
00:05:34,405 --> 00:05:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so I totally thought you were.</font>

82
00:05:37,705 --> 00:05:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wouldn't call it relaxed.
More like insulting.</font>

83
00:05:40,672 --> 00:05:42,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! I have an idea!</font>

84
00:05:42,205 --> 00:05:44,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, can you also tell him</font>

85
00:05:44,072 --> 00:05:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to come back home?</font>

86
00:05:46,305 --> 00:05:47,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

87
00:05:47,305 --> 00:05:50,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He doesn't listen to a word I say.</font>

88
00:05:50,705 --> 00:05:53,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's a real smart-ass, that <i>man-brat.</i></font>

89
00:05:54,305 --> 00:05:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Man-brat?</i></font>

90
00:05:57,072 --> 00:05:59,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's my nickname for Hisashi.</font>

91
00:06:00,072 --> 00:06:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He looks older than he is,
but inside he's still a brat.</font>

92
00:06:03,905 --> 00:06:05,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I call him <i>man-brat.</i></font>

93
00:06:06,505 --> 00:06:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see. He sure is.</font>

94
00:06:18,072 --> 00:06:20,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-oh.
I've got to get back to the office.</font>

95
00:06:20,905 --> 00:06:22,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Now?</font>

96
00:06:22,905 --> 00:06:26,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.
I'm an editor at an information magazine.</font>

97
00:06:27,305 --> 00:06:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's always like this before a deadline.</font>

98
00:06:29,605 --> 00:06:32,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a real pain. Bye.</font>

99
00:06:50,605 --> 00:06:54,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yuri sure was cool.</i></font>

100
00:06:55,872 --> 00:06:57,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's beautiful as well.</font>

101
00:07:09,505 --> 00:07:13,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder if
I'll be like that in a few years too?</font>

102
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The hell you will.</i></font>

103
00:07:16,505 --> 00:07:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

104
00:07:18,305 --> 00:07:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is he...</font>

105
00:07:24,972 --> 00:07:29,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn him!
I got so used to hearing his insults.</font>

106
00:07:29,205 --> 00:07:31,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're such a jerk, Uehara!</font>

107
00:07:44,205 --> 00:07:45,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a minute...</font>

108
00:07:46,939 --> 00:07:49,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's coming back, isn't he?</font>

109
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:53,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's not going back to his home,
right?</font>

110
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See ya!</font>

111
00:08:07,205 --> 00:08:10,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? W... wait! Wait!</font>

112
00:08:13,105 --> 00:08:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This month's $1,500, please.</font>

113
00:08:17,572 --> 00:08:18,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah!</font>

114
00:08:19,939 --> 00:08:23,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No! No way! I can't pay!</font>

115
00:08:23,705 --> 00:08:24,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What'll I do?</font>

116
00:08:26,872 --> 00:08:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll keep Uehara here
by winning him over with food.</font>

117
00:08:31,605 --> 00:08:34,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The amount of food is more important
than the taste.</font>

118
00:08:35,672 --> 00:08:38,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll make him tons of dishes.</font>

119
00:08:48,205 --> 00:08:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Popular Recipes for Restoring Health
and Building Strength</font>

120
00:08:55,005 --> 00:08:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">STAMINA BUILDING POTATO SALAD</font>

121
00:09:01,505 --> 00:09:02,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's see now...</font>

122
00:09:11,105 --> 00:09:12,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that scared me.</font>

123
00:09:30,205 --> 00:09:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yum!</font>

124
00:09:40,171 --> 00:09:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MEGUROGAOKA HIGH SCHOOL</font>

125
00:10:06,839 --> 00:10:10,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They're really dating? What a shock!</font>

126
00:10:10,405 --> 00:10:12,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Totally!
How could Uehara choose Yoshikawa?</font>

127
00:10:12,939 --> 00:10:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you believe it?</font>

128
00:10:14,572 --> 00:10:15,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yo! Morning, Daichi.</font>

129
00:10:16,005 --> 00:10:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Morning.
-Morning.</font>

130
00:10:34,105 --> 00:10:35,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good morning, Marina.</font>

131
00:10:36,772 --> 00:10:39,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hiro, did you prep for Algebra II?</font>

132
00:10:39,405 --> 00:10:40,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I did.</font>

133
00:10:40,505 --> 00:10:43,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, there's a part I wanted to ask about.</font>

134
00:10:43,205 --> 00:10:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where?</font>

135
00:10:48,772 --> 00:10:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We've got Music next. Let's go together.</font>

136
00:10:54,505 --> 00:10:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

137
00:10:59,939 --> 00:11:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Marina.</font>

138
00:11:04,605 --> 00:11:05,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

139
00:11:18,605 --> 00:11:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry... Daichi.</font>

140
00:11:20,705 --> 00:11:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Yes?</font>

141
00:11:22,572 --> 00:11:24,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, nothing... I just...</font>

142
00:11:25,605 --> 00:11:27,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao, are you--
-Marina's getting away.</font>

143
00:11:27,705 --> 00:11:29,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. We can talk later.</font>

144
00:12:23,872 --> 00:12:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Eek!
-Eek!</font>

145
00:12:27,505 --> 00:12:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn you!</font>

146
00:12:36,305 --> 00:12:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit following me.</font>

147
00:12:39,605 --> 00:12:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you're ignoring me?</font>

148
00:12:46,872 --> 00:12:48,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because you lied to me.</font>

149
00:12:52,605 --> 00:12:55,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really are Uehara's girlfriend.</font>

150
00:12:57,772 --> 00:13:00,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She is my girlfriend.</font>

151
00:13:01,805 --> 00:13:03,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How did you find out?</font>

152
00:13:04,305 --> 00:13:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara of the top three has a girlfriend.</font>

153
00:13:07,305 --> 00:13:09,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That kind of news spreads like wildfire.</font>

154
00:13:10,205 --> 00:13:12,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But, you see--
-Don't get me wrong.</font>

155
00:13:14,405 --> 00:13:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not angry
that you're Uehara's girlfriend.</font>

156
00:13:19,705 --> 00:13:20,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

157
00:13:21,405 --> 00:13:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm pissed at you</font>

158
00:13:24,105 --> 00:13:26,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because you lied to me
that there was nothing between you two.</font>

159
00:13:30,205 --> 00:13:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know it's not easy to tell me</font>

160
00:13:32,605 --> 00:13:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because I'm always talking about Uehara.</font>

161
00:13:36,472 --> 00:13:39,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you and I have known each other
for so much longer.</font>

162
00:13:39,672 --> 00:13:42,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I thought I was your best friend.</font>

163
00:13:44,672 --> 00:13:47,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's like you're putting up a front,</font>

164
00:13:47,705 --> 00:13:50,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but in your heart, you're blowing me off.</font>

165
00:13:51,705 --> 00:13:53,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina...</font>

166
00:13:59,805 --> 00:14:01,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come you're going to cry?</font>

167
00:14:03,505 --> 00:14:04,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

168
00:14:14,105 --> 00:14:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tell me everything from now on, OK?
I'll tell you everything about me too.</font>

169
00:14:19,672 --> 00:14:22,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK.
-Good.</font>

170
00:14:26,405 --> 00:14:28,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I...
-Yes?</font>

171
00:14:29,605 --> 00:14:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To tell the truth,
we're pretending to be dating.</font>

172
00:14:33,605 --> 00:14:34,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

173
00:14:36,105 --> 00:14:37,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh. Class is going to start.</font>

174
00:14:38,305 --> 00:14:39,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Hey!</font>

175
00:14:39,672 --> 00:14:44,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Wait!
You'd better fill me in later! Wait!</font>

176
00:14:44,472 --> 00:14:45,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold on a second!</font>

177
00:14:45,605 --> 00:14:47,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean
you and Uehara are living there together?</font>

178
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Who told you?</font>

179
00:14:49,605 --> 00:14:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.
So to keep people from finding out</font>

180
00:14:52,505 --> 00:14:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that they're living together,
he said to pretend that they're dating.</font>

181
00:14:55,939 --> 00:15:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought he was a Prince Charming,
but she says he's a stuck-up jerk.</font>

182
00:15:00,605 --> 00:15:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, that's absolutely right!</font>

183
00:15:02,305 --> 00:15:04,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's worse, he's got everyone fooled.</font>

184
00:15:05,039 --> 00:15:06,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't he awful, Mitsuishi?</font>

185
00:15:06,605 --> 00:15:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, but don't you think</font>

186
00:15:08,205 --> 00:15:10,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the bigger problem is
the fact you're living with a guy?</font>

187
00:15:11,039 --> 00:15:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There haven't been any problems yet.</font>

188
00:15:13,472 --> 00:15:14,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What're you talking about?</font>

189
00:15:15,805 --> 00:15:16,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course there has.</font>

190
00:15:16,805 --> 00:15:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you taking that to Uehara
at the hospital?</font>

191
00:15:19,205 --> 00:15:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep.</font>

192
00:15:20,305 --> 00:15:24,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's part of my plan to use food
to keep him from leaving.</font>

193
00:15:24,105 --> 00:15:26,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you were up all night cooking.</font>

194
00:15:26,805 --> 00:15:28,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How did you know?</font>

195
00:15:28,405 --> 00:15:29,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Rings under your eyes.</font>

196
00:15:32,905 --> 00:15:37,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's such a big eater,
I thought I'd better make a lot.</font>

197
00:15:37,505 --> 00:15:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It took forever.</font>

198
00:15:39,205 --> 00:15:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, Nao, I think you like Uehara.</font>

199
00:15:42,405 --> 00:15:45,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Of course I don't!</font>

200
00:15:45,505 --> 00:15:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never said anything like that.</font>

201
00:15:47,605 --> 00:15:48,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's what's called</font>

202
00:15:49,005 --> 00:15:51,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">getting to a man's heart
through his stomach.</font>

203
00:15:51,305 --> 00:15:52,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

204
00:15:52,605 --> 00:15:54,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you I'm not!</font>

205
00:15:55,505 --> 00:15:58,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara has a real girlfriend.</font>

206
00:15:58,505 --> 00:15:59,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-What? Who?</font>

207
00:16:01,672 --> 00:16:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">His older brother's wife.</font>

208
00:16:05,205 --> 00:16:09,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's super pretty.
So cheerful and kind too.</font>

209
00:16:09,839 --> 00:16:11,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Competent at her job as well.</font>

210
00:16:12,605 --> 00:16:16,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A real grown-up woman.</font>

211
00:16:19,205 --> 00:16:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not visiting him.</font>

212
00:16:20,472 --> 00:16:21,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why not?</font>

213
00:16:21,605 --> 00:16:24,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because she can take care of him.</font>

214
00:16:24,672 --> 00:16:26,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep. She'll do it.</font>

215
00:16:26,972 --> 00:16:30,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She'll take care of him, so I'm not.</font>

216
00:16:30,305 --> 00:16:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to eat this myself.</font>

217
00:16:32,605 --> 00:16:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not going. Nope. Not going.</font>

218
00:16:37,072 --> 00:16:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everyone I know is so blind to love.</font>

219
00:16:43,672 --> 00:16:44,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You are too.</font>

220
00:16:45,772 --> 00:16:46,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you say something?</font>

221
00:16:48,405 --> 00:16:49,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

222
00:16:59,405 --> 00:17:02,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe I'll just look in on him.</font>

223
00:17:08,905 --> 00:17:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">God damn him!</font>

224
00:17:21,472 --> 00:17:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yo.</font>

225
00:17:24,505 --> 00:17:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that supposed to mean?</font>

226
00:17:26,605 --> 00:17:28,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You could at least
tell me you were released.</font>

227
00:17:29,039 --> 00:17:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't have your number.</font>

228
00:17:32,205 --> 00:17:33,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh...</font>

229
00:17:36,605 --> 00:17:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ADDED TO MY CONTACTS</font>

230
00:17:39,105 --> 00:17:40,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

231
00:17:42,305 --> 00:17:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't always be contacting me.
I hate Line and texting.</font>

232
00:17:47,039 --> 00:17:49,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why would I contact you
if I didn't have a reason?</font>

233
00:17:50,972 --> 00:17:52,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that?</font>

234
00:17:53,505 --> 00:17:57,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... That's your dinner.</font>

235
00:17:57,972 --> 00:17:59,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll have it for a midnight snack.</font>

236
00:18:00,171 --> 00:18:03,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You should have dinner before that.</font>

237
00:18:06,305 --> 00:18:08,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me that...</font>

238
00:18:15,772 --> 00:18:17,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You ate it all!</font>

239
00:18:22,572 --> 00:18:24,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

240
00:18:24,505 --> 00:18:27,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You broke the rules!
You ate my food without permission!</font>

241
00:18:27,472 --> 00:18:28,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh...</font>

242
00:18:30,939 --> 00:18:34,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm recovering so I made an exception.</font>

243
00:18:36,105 --> 00:18:37,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

244
00:18:39,105 --> 00:18:43,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That ticks me off!
Who said he could make an exception?</font>

245
00:18:44,039 --> 00:18:47,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And how can he eat that much
when he's supposed to be recovering?</font>

246
00:18:55,205 --> 00:18:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He actually did come back here.</font>

247
00:19:00,939 --> 00:19:05,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn it all.
And I was enjoying living alone so much.</font>

248
00:19:13,905 --> 00:19:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's right.</font>

249
00:19:21,105 --> 00:19:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MOM</font>

250
00:19:22,705 --> 00:19:24,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's Mom.</font>

251
00:19:24,772 --> 00:19:26,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Are you eating nutritiously?</i></font>

252
00:19:26,672 --> 00:19:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You wouldn't believe it,
but I'm cooking for myself.</font>

253
00:19:30,872 --> 00:19:32,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Well, that's good to hear.</i></font>

254
00:19:32,672 --> 00:19:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Oh. You're not forgetting
what your real job as a student is, right?</i></font>

255
00:19:36,205 --> 00:19:37,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got that covered too.</font>

256
00:19:37,805 --> 00:19:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so much easier to study
when I'm living alone.</font>

257
00:19:41,872 --> 00:19:45,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Oh, is that so?
Are you ready for your next final--</i></font>

258
00:19:45,405 --> 00:19:49,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Trust me, Mom. I've changed.</font>

259
00:19:49,205 --> 00:19:51,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I might even make it
into the top half of the class.</font>

260
00:19:52,039 --> 00:19:53,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Really? That's great.</i></font>

261
00:19:54,105 --> 00:19:56,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Your father and I talked this over.</i></font>

262
00:19:56,705 --> 00:20:00,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>If you're not in the top half,
then you won't be living alone anymore.</i></font>

263
00:20:00,205 --> 00:20:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. Piece of cake.</font>

264
00:20:03,705 --> 00:20:07,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Really? I'm looking forward to it.</i></font>

265
00:20:07,972 --> 00:20:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. Bye.</font>

266
00:20:15,805 --> 00:20:18,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did I really say, <i>piece of cake?</i></font>

267
00:20:21,405 --> 00:20:23,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When are finals?</font>

268
00:20:30,305 --> 00:20:32,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From Tuesday.</font>

269
00:20:33,305 --> 00:20:35,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today's Saturday.</font>

270
00:20:35,505 --> 00:20:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Saturday, Sunday, Monday.</font>

271
00:20:38,905 --> 00:20:39,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no!</font>

272
00:20:40,972 --> 00:20:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm more likely to be out of here
than Uehara is.</font>

273
00:20:47,305 --> 00:20:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to study!</font>

274
00:20:50,905 --> 00:20:53,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My pencils! Oops!</font>

275
00:21:01,305 --> 00:21:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome home.
Must be hard working so early.</font>

276
00:21:04,405 --> 00:21:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, thanks.</font>

277
00:21:10,171 --> 00:21:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Were you up all night?</font>

278
00:21:12,405 --> 00:21:14,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tests are coming up.</font>

279
00:21:14,205 --> 00:21:17,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. Must be tough being stupid.</font>

280
00:21:23,705 --> 00:21:24,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you OK?</font>

281
00:21:27,505 --> 00:21:28,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah!</font>

282
00:21:30,305 --> 00:21:31,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got you!</font>

283
00:21:32,005 --> 00:21:34,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! Tutor me, please!</font>

284
00:21:34,805 --> 00:21:36,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No.
-What?</font>

285
00:21:37,305 --> 00:21:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why not?
-It'd be a real pain.</font>

286
00:21:39,572 --> 00:21:44,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you seem like a poor learner.
All it would do is exhaust me.</font>

287
00:21:44,405 --> 00:21:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All you do is complain.</font>

288
00:21:47,572 --> 00:21:50,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really are a <i>man-brat.</i></font>

289
00:21:58,205 --> 00:21:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you and Yuri...</font>

290
00:22:05,205 --> 00:22:06,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget it.</font>

291
00:22:25,005 --> 00:22:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara
Yuri's Married-Uehara's Older Brother</font>

292
00:22:42,005 --> 00:22:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no! I haven't made any progress!</font>

293
00:22:51,872 --> 00:22:54,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't understand this!</font>

294
00:22:57,205 --> 00:22:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't understand this!</font>

295
00:23:01,872 --> 00:23:04,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't understand...</font>

296
00:23:10,605 --> 00:23:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">FINALS</font>

297
00:23:14,472 --> 00:23:15,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, I can't.</font>

298
00:23:18,405 --> 00:23:21,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We've got a practice game today.</font>

299
00:23:22,505 --> 00:23:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see. Yeah, I guess you're busy.</font>

300
00:23:27,205 --> 00:23:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've always been the type</font>

301
00:23:28,872 --> 00:23:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that won't start
until you're up against a wall.</font>

302
00:23:32,505 --> 00:23:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Summer vacation homework,
research projects and book reports.</font>

303
00:23:38,605 --> 00:23:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. Your somersault practice too.</font>

304
00:23:42,872 --> 00:23:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You helped me with all those, Daichi.</font>

305
00:23:46,305 --> 00:23:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'd be nice
if you appreciated me a little more.</font>

306
00:23:49,705 --> 00:23:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I do, Daichi.</font>

307
00:23:51,205 --> 00:23:53,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I totally appreciate what you've done.</font>

308
00:23:54,772 --> 00:23:55,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'll do it.</font>

309
00:23:56,939 --> 00:24:01,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I really do need
to stop depending on you.</font>

310
00:24:04,872 --> 00:24:05,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

311
00:24:05,872 --> 00:24:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing. Do your best. Bye.</font>

312
00:24:09,305 --> 00:24:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. Thanks. Bye.</font>

313
00:24:30,605 --> 00:24:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's Yuri.</font>

314
00:24:40,705 --> 00:24:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was close.</font>

315
00:24:47,605 --> 00:24:50,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OA times OB cosine C</font>

316
00:24:50,405 --> 00:24:55,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">minus one half, parentheses, A times B...</font>

317
00:24:56,772 --> 00:24:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What was it again?</font>

318
00:24:59,805 --> 00:25:01,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! It's vector.</font>

319
00:25:01,505 --> 00:25:03,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Hey there.</font>

320
00:25:03,305 --> 00:25:04,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri!</font>

321
00:25:09,039 --> 00:25:12,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yum! It's delicious!
-This is great.</font>

322
00:25:13,405 --> 00:25:14,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's delicious.</font>

323
00:25:14,772 --> 00:25:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so glad I ran into you, Nao.</font>

324
00:25:17,972 --> 00:25:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I left him a message
to say I was going to drop by</font>

325
00:25:20,772 --> 00:25:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but he never called back.</font>

326
00:25:23,039 --> 00:25:24,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could you call him for me, Nao?</font>

327
00:25:25,005 --> 00:25:26,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't get in unless he's there.</font>

328
00:25:27,805 --> 00:25:31,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I think he's working today.
Probably...</font>

329
00:25:31,839 --> 00:25:34,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? He is?</font>

330
00:25:34,305 --> 00:25:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn him. Why can't he just call?
He's such a pain.</font>

331
00:25:40,705 --> 00:25:43,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, Yuri...</font>

332
00:25:43,205 --> 00:25:45,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you call me Yuririn?</font>

333
00:25:46,205 --> 00:25:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuririn?</font>

334
00:25:47,205 --> 00:25:49,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.
And you don't have to talk so polite.</font>

335
00:25:52,205 --> 00:25:55,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then, Yuririn...</font>

336
00:25:56,039 --> 00:25:58,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes? What is it?</font>

337
00:25:58,505 --> 00:25:59,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

338
00:26:00,039 --> 00:26:04,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara... Is he...</font>

339
00:26:08,205 --> 00:26:10,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did he say something about me?</font>

340
00:26:14,305 --> 00:26:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But... when he's with you,
he seems different than usual.</font>

341
00:26:22,305 --> 00:26:24,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He looks so pained.</font>

342
00:26:26,672 --> 00:26:29,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I was his first love.</font>

343
00:26:30,972 --> 00:26:31,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

344
00:26:33,205 --> 00:26:35,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Takuya and Hisashi's family
and mine were friends,</i></font>

345
00:26:35,672 --> 00:26:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>so we got along really well.</i></font>

346
00:26:38,205 --> 00:26:41,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The three of us would always
play around as kids.</i></font>

347
00:26:41,572 --> 00:26:47,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>But when their parents died,
they became depressed.</i></font>

348
00:26:49,705 --> 00:26:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I said I'd be their mother instead.</i></font>

349
00:26:53,105 --> 00:26:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So I was always over at their house.</i></font>

350
00:26:56,772 --> 00:27:02,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then I fell in love with him...
Takuya, I mean.</font>

351
00:27:03,705 --> 00:27:05,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hisashi is like a little brother to me.</font>

352
00:27:06,505 --> 00:27:11,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had absolutely no clue
that he had a crush on me.</font>

353
00:27:13,305 --> 00:27:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Not long after, we got married</i></font>

354
00:27:16,105 --> 00:27:19,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>and I was living in the Uehara house.</i></font>

355
00:27:20,072 --> 00:27:21,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>He told me.</i></font>

356
00:27:23,105 --> 00:27:27,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"I can't live with the woman I like
and her husband."</i></font>

357
00:27:29,705 --> 00:27:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It must have been hard for him.
I really felt bad about it.</font>

358
00:27:36,872 --> 00:27:38,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...</font>

359
00:27:39,072 --> 00:27:40,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, seriously!</font>

360
00:27:40,305 --> 00:27:42,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Takuya and I were newlyweds
and so in love.</font>

361
00:27:42,872 --> 00:27:44,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We couldn't help it.</font>

362
00:27:44,505 --> 00:27:47,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he liked me,
then he should have said sooner!</font>

363
00:27:47,905 --> 00:27:49,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I guess that</font>

364
00:27:49,972 --> 00:27:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">getting drunk and kissing him a bunch
probably gave him the wrong idea.</font>

365
00:27:53,772 --> 00:27:54,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

366
00:27:54,772 --> 00:27:57,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear.
I'll kiss anyone when I'm drunk.</font>

367
00:27:57,972 --> 00:27:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, really.</font>

368
00:27:59,305 --> 00:28:01,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure I've kissed Hisashi 20 times.</font>

369
00:28:01,705 --> 00:28:03,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? 20 times?</font>

370
00:28:04,672 --> 00:28:06,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you jealous?</font>

371
00:28:07,972 --> 00:28:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. There's nothing between us--</font>

372
00:28:10,605 --> 00:28:12,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, yeah. Sure. OK!</font>

373
00:28:12,305 --> 00:28:16,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since I've come all this way,
I may as well see his place.</font>

374
00:28:16,872 --> 00:28:19,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What? Wait! Wait!</font>

375
00:28:22,305 --> 00:28:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait!</font>

376
00:28:25,105 --> 00:28:26,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You forgot this!</font>

377
00:28:26,505 --> 00:28:27,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold on!</font>

378
00:28:29,305 --> 00:28:31,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. I'm OK.</font>

379
00:28:32,505 --> 00:28:33,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Seriously, I'm just fine.</font>

380
00:28:34,039 --> 00:28:36,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's alright.
Don't push yourself when you're still ill.</font>

381
00:28:36,605 --> 00:28:38,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm good. I really am all better.</font>

382
00:28:38,505 --> 00:28:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take the day off and relax.</font>

383
00:28:40,705 --> 00:28:41,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

384
00:28:42,705 --> 00:28:43,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

385
00:28:46,005 --> 00:28:47,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He hung up?</font>

386
00:28:57,072 --> 00:29:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If they're going to cancel,
I wish they'd tell us sooner.</font>

387
00:29:00,605 --> 00:29:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They said they caught the flu.</font>

388
00:29:02,305 --> 00:29:04,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Seriously?</font>

389
00:29:04,105 --> 00:29:05,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

390
00:29:06,005 --> 00:29:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-See you later.
-See you.</font>

391
00:29:12,005 --> 00:29:12,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

392
00:29:13,005 --> 00:29:14,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Daichi. Where are you headed?</font>

393
00:29:15,039 --> 00:29:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's place.</font>

394
00:29:16,105 --> 00:29:19,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Our game was cancelled,
so I'm going over to tutor her.</font>

395
00:29:19,705 --> 00:29:20,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Later.</font>

396
00:29:23,305 --> 00:29:25,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's place?</font>

397
00:29:25,305 --> 00:29:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh...
There'll be trouble if Uehara's there.</font>

398
00:29:28,605 --> 00:29:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Serious trouble.
Daichi's kind of old-fashioned.</font>

399
00:29:32,605 --> 00:29:36,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If he found out that Nao and Uehara are
living together...</font>

400
00:29:36,305 --> 00:29:37,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What would happen?</font>

401
00:29:37,405 --> 00:29:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Run, Mitsuishi!</font>

402
00:29:39,672 --> 00:29:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, my god!</font>

403
00:29:40,705 --> 00:29:41,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Seriously?</font>

404
00:29:42,605 --> 00:29:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's jump rope.</font>

405
00:29:46,905 --> 00:29:49,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on, Mitsuishi. Hurry up!</font>

406
00:29:54,305 --> 00:29:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

407
00:31:13,105 --> 00:31:14,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yo!</font>

408
00:31:21,805 --> 00:31:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uh...
-Uh...</font>

409
00:31:23,572 --> 00:31:24,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who are you?</font>

410
00:31:25,572 --> 00:31:27,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't this Yoshikawa Nao's place?</font>

411
00:31:29,405 --> 00:31:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">God damn her.</font>

412
00:31:35,205 --> 00:31:37,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aren't you the junior, Uehara?</font>

413
00:31:38,705 --> 00:31:40,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. What of it?</font>

414
00:31:41,405 --> 00:31:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing in Nao's place?</font>

415
00:31:47,039 --> 00:31:50,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello there! We're coming in, Uehara.</font>

416
00:31:50,505 --> 00:31:51,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What're you two doing?</font>

417
00:31:51,772 --> 00:31:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Leave this to us.</font>

418
00:31:53,305 --> 00:31:55,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Hey!</font>

419
00:31:55,205 --> 00:31:57,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! I'm not finished talking to you!</font>

420
00:31:57,205 --> 00:31:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi, don't get so worked up, OK?</font>

421
00:31:59,105 --> 00:32:00,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, guys!</font>

422
00:32:00,072 --> 00:32:02,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got milk tea.
Why don't we take a break?</font>

423
00:32:02,772 --> 00:32:04,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hey! That's mine!
-What?</font>

424
00:32:04,605 --> 00:32:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Give it back. Give it back.
-Wait! Stop!</font>

425
00:32:06,705 --> 00:32:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! Are you and Nao--</font>

426
00:32:09,872 --> 00:32:10,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm drinking this!</font>

427
00:32:10,872 --> 00:32:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's mine. Don't you dare!</font>

428
00:32:12,072 --> 00:32:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who cares about that--</font>

429
00:32:13,405 --> 00:32:15,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now, now. Take a deep breath.</font>

430
00:32:15,405 --> 00:32:16,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get out of my way, Mitsuishi!</font>

431
00:32:16,772 --> 00:32:19,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Look at all these people!</font>

432
00:32:20,005 --> 00:32:21,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What fun!</font>

433
00:32:27,105 --> 00:32:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nice to meet all of you.
-Nao!</font>

434
00:32:28,505 --> 00:32:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Hisashi's sister-in-law, Yuri.</font>

435
00:32:31,305 --> 00:32:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao...</font>

436
00:32:33,305 --> 00:32:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-God damn you!
-Are you all Hisashi's friends?</font>

437
00:32:35,405 --> 00:32:36,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course they're not!</font>

438
00:32:36,939 --> 00:32:37,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

439
00:32:38,405 --> 00:32:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, are you Uehara's girlfriend?</font>

440
00:32:40,805 --> 00:32:41,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh...</font>

441
00:32:42,205 --> 00:32:43,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi! Daichi!</font>

442
00:32:43,205 --> 00:32:45,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao's living with him,
but she's not his girl--</font>

443
00:32:45,105 --> 00:32:46,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Living together?</font>

444
00:32:47,305 --> 00:32:48,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're living with Hisashi?</font>

445
00:32:49,705 --> 00:32:51,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew it! You're his girlfriend.</font>

446
00:32:51,305 --> 00:32:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I'm not!</font>

447
00:32:53,105 --> 00:32:54,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We <i>are living together--</i></font>

448
00:32:54,672 --> 00:32:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Pretend! They're pretending dating!</font>

449
00:32:56,205 --> 00:32:57,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right!</font>

450
00:32:57,205 --> 00:32:59,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why do you have to live together
if you're just pretending?</font>

451
00:32:59,872 --> 00:33:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a minute!</font>

452
00:33:01,205 --> 00:33:02,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you after her body, Hisashi?</font>

453
00:33:03,005 --> 00:33:03,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After her body?</font>

454
00:33:03,972 --> 00:33:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No way! How shameful!
-It's total chaos!</font>

455
00:33:08,405 --> 00:33:11,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell are you thinking--</font>

456
00:33:11,105 --> 00:33:12,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shut up!</font>

457
00:33:18,105 --> 00:33:19,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll tell you everything.</font>

458
00:33:22,972 --> 00:33:25,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So everybody, just shut up.</font>

459
00:33:28,905 --> 00:33:29,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow!</font>

460
00:33:34,572 --> 00:33:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the story. All of it.</font>

461
00:33:39,005 --> 00:33:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yay!</font>

462
00:33:45,305 --> 00:33:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got no interest in her at all.</font>

463
00:33:47,605 --> 00:33:49,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn, you're awfully frank.</font>

464
00:33:49,205 --> 00:33:53,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She feels the same about me.
We're simply living together.</font>

465
00:33:53,505 --> 00:33:54,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right?</font>

466
00:33:55,105 --> 00:33:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes... That's exactly right.</font>

467
00:33:57,705 --> 00:33:59,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides,
she's moving to the dorms in April.</font>

468
00:34:00,505 --> 00:34:03,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I plan to save enough money
to move by then.</font>

469
00:34:06,105 --> 00:34:10,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I'd like to continue...
living together like this.</font>

470
00:34:18,505 --> 00:34:19,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

471
00:34:21,105 --> 00:34:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is the first time...
Uehara and I have lived alone.</font>

472
00:34:27,872 --> 00:34:30,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're trying to figure things out,
so we're alike in that.</font>

473
00:34:30,972 --> 00:34:31,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not like you.</font>

474
00:34:31,939 --> 00:34:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We always fight,</font>

475
00:34:34,705 --> 00:34:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but since we're alike,
we understand each other.</font>

476
00:34:39,505 --> 00:34:40,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's reassuring.</font>

477
00:34:45,305 --> 00:34:50,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, I know you're worried about us,</font>

478
00:34:52,505 --> 00:34:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but...</font>

479
00:34:55,905 --> 00:34:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">please let us continue living together.
Please.</font>

480
00:35:03,672 --> 00:35:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please.</font>

481
00:35:20,171 --> 00:35:21,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

482
00:35:22,572 --> 00:35:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry I kept it secret
that we were living together.</font>

483
00:35:29,072 --> 00:35:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It doesn't bother me at all.</font>

484
00:35:31,305 --> 00:35:33,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I understand what Hisashi's situation is.</font>

485
00:35:34,472 --> 00:35:37,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since it's with you, Nao,
I feel good about it.</font>

486
00:35:37,705 --> 00:35:39,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri.</font>

487
00:35:40,705 --> 00:35:43,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, see you later. Take care of Hisashi.</font>

488
00:35:49,105 --> 00:35:51,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Yes?</font>

489
00:35:51,705 --> 00:35:54,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought Uehara and Yuri
were having an affair.</font>

490
00:35:55,305 --> 00:35:58,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I misunderstood.
-How could you do that?</font>

491
00:35:59,039 --> 00:36:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I was half right.</font>

492
00:36:01,305 --> 00:36:02,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

493
00:36:17,805 --> 00:36:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

494
00:36:19,305 --> 00:36:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't understand
your way of thinking at all.</font>

495
00:36:22,772 --> 00:36:23,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

496
00:36:24,805 --> 00:36:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you live with a total stranger?
And she's a girl too?</font>

497
00:36:30,605 --> 00:36:33,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What business is it of yours?
-Are you doing this because it's Nao?</font>

498
00:36:34,972 --> 00:36:36,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because you think
she'll be easy to control?</font>

499
00:36:40,105 --> 00:36:41,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And so what if I do?</font>

500
00:36:43,405 --> 00:36:45,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the type</font>

501
00:36:45,905 --> 00:36:48,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that hurts others without even knowing it.</font>

502
00:36:50,205 --> 00:36:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What does that mean?</font>

503
00:36:51,205 --> 00:36:52,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Exactly like it sounds.</font>

504
00:37:02,505 --> 00:37:03,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

505
00:37:05,972 --> 00:37:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi... You're angry, aren't you?</font>

506
00:37:13,405 --> 00:37:15,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really sorry I didn't tell you.</font>

507
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:24,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If anything happens,
you come straight over to my place.</font>

508
00:37:25,605 --> 00:37:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

509
00:37:46,505 --> 00:37:48,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks for everything.</font>

510
00:37:48,705 --> 00:37:52,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Christ!
You've been nothing but trouble for me.</font>

511
00:37:52,572 --> 00:37:54,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How dare you!
Quit acting like it's all my fault.</font>

512
00:37:54,972 --> 00:37:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You brought them all over here, right?</font>

513
00:37:58,305 --> 00:38:00,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. I'm sorry.</font>

514
00:38:03,872 --> 00:38:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, at least it all worked out.</font>

515
00:38:11,105 --> 00:38:12,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What?</font>

516
00:38:12,705 --> 00:38:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">High five.</font>

517
00:38:22,305 --> 00:38:25,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow!
Why do you have to use such force?</font>

518
00:38:25,105 --> 00:38:26,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway,
we can breathe a little easier now.</font>

519
00:38:27,005 --> 00:38:30,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really are happy-go-lucky.
I'm going to bed.</font>

520
00:38:33,672 --> 00:38:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no!</font>

521
00:38:35,772 --> 00:38:36,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?</font>

522
00:38:38,772 --> 00:38:40,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Tests...
-Huh?</font>

523
00:38:41,305 --> 00:38:45,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I don't get a good score on my tests,
I'll have to go back home.</font>

524
00:38:46,505 --> 00:38:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you kidding me?</font>

525
00:38:48,105 --> 00:38:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you before!
How come you can't understand this?</font>

526
00:38:51,405 --> 00:38:53,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't help it if I can't understand.
It's not my fault.</font>

527
00:38:54,005 --> 00:38:55,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Use the formula, damn it.</font>

528
